label: not accredited
description: Abstract prepared at a facility WITHOUT CoC accreditation of its cancer program

label: accredited, analytic abstract
description: ANALYTIC abstract prepared at facility WITH CoC accreditation of its cancer program (Includes Class of Case codes 10-22)

label: accredited, non-analytic abstract
description: NON-ANALYTIC abstract prepared at facility WITH CoC accreditation of its cancer program (Includes Class of Case codes 30-43 and 99, plus code 00 which CoC considers analytic but does not require to be staged)
